textBody:
Antwerp is a city in Belgium and capital of the Antwerp province.

Antwerp may also refer to:

;In Belgium
* Antwerp (district)
* Antwerp (province)

;In the United States
* Antwerp, Ohio
* Antwerp Township, Michigan
* Antwerp (village), New York
* Antwerp (town), New York

;In Australia
*Antwerp, Victoria

Other 

*Port of Antwerp
*Antwerp (Quest For Glory), a monster in the Quest for Glory computer role-playing game series
* Antwerp (pigeon), a domestic breed of Rock Pigeon which originated in the Belgian city
*Royal Antwerp FC, a football club in the Belgian city of Antwerp
*Antwerp (novel), by Roberto Bolaño
*Antwerp (poem), by Ford Madox Hueffer (later known as Ford Madox Ford)
